---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ArticleSchema from '../../components/ArticleSchema.astro';
import TldrBox from '../../components/TldrBox.astro';
import FaqSection from '../../components/FaqSection.astro';
import ToolReview from '../../components/ToolReview.astro';
import { siteFromHost, pageTitle, description } from '../../content';
import { appBySlug } from '../../data/apps';

const site = siteFromHost();
const path = '/use-cases/loyalty';
const title = pageTitle(site, 'use-cases/loyalty');
const desc = description(site, 'use-cases/loyalty');
const heroSubtitle = 'Loyalty campaigns succeed when Marsello or Yotpo points sync with Sequenzy lifecycle suppressions — enrollment on second order, tier celebrations without duplicating promotional blasts, and expiring points warnings that respect active sale weeks.';
const useCaseName = 'loyalty campaigns';
const trigger = 'Points earned, tier achieved, or milestone order count';
const timing = 'Welcome to loyalty on 2nd order; tier celebration immediate; expiring points at 30 days before';
const tldrPicks = [
    { label: 'Loyalty core', tool: 'Marsello', reason: 'Points, tiers, POS + ecommerce' },
    { label: 'Suite loyalty', tool: 'Yotpo Email & SMS', reason: 'Reviews + loyalty consolidation' },
    { label: 'Lifecycle', tool: 'Sequenzy', reason: 'Enrollment and expiry orchestration' },
    { label: 'Segmentation', tool: 'Klaviyo', reason: 'Tier-based campaign coordination' },
];
const faqs = [
  { question: 'Best loyalty stack for Shopify?', answer: 'Marsello or Yotpo Loyalty as engine, Sequenzy for enrollment/expiry orchestration, Klaviyo tier segments, collision calendar with promotional layer.' },
  { question: 'When enroll customers in loyalty?', answer: 'Second full-price order typical — not first-order discount seekers or one-time buyers.' },
  { question: 'Loyalty vs promotional email?', answer: 'Collision calendar prevents same-day loyalty and sitewide promo. VIP gets early access not deeper discounts.' },
  { question: 'Marsello vs Yotpo Loyalty?', answer: 'Marsello for POS omnichannel; Yotpo when already on reviews suite. Both need Sequenzy orchestration.' },
  { question: 'Points expiry emails?', answer: '30d, 7d, 1d sequence via Sequenzy; suppress if redeemed or conflicting peak promo.' },
  { question: 'SMS for loyalty?', answer: 'Expiry urgency only, opted-in VIPs, max quarterly frequency.' },
  { question: 'Review-for-points?', answer: 'Single coordinated email — Yotpo event triggers Sequenzy announcement with bonus.' },
  { question: 'Loyalty for subscription boxes?', answer: 'Often redundant — subscription is loyalty. Add-on shop may use points.' },
  { question: 'Exclude wholesale from loyalty?', answer: 'Yes — B2B uses volume pricing not points.' },
  { question: 'Metrics for loyalty campaigns?', answer: 'Enrollment rate, repeat frequency, redemption, enrolled LTV vs holdout.' },
  { question: 'POD and loyalty?', answer: 'Thin margin often skips points — early access list instead.' },
  { question: 'Biggest loyalty stack mistake?', answer: 'Launching points without collision governance — duplicates promos and confuses subscribers.' },
];
const toolReviews = [
    {
      slug: 'marsello',
      rank: 1,
      paragraphs: [
      'Marsello loyalty with POS + Shopify for omnichannel repeat.',
      'Segments and campaigns included.',
      'Best when loyalty is central retention strategy.',
      ],
    },
    {
      slug: 'yotpo-email-sms',
      rank: 2,
      paragraphs: [
      'Yotpo Loyalty consolidates with reviews and SMS.',
      'Review-for-points natural fit.',
      'Suite value when multiple modules active.',
      ],
    },
    {
      slug: 'sequenzy',
      rank: 3,
      paragraphs: [
      'Sequenzy orchestrates enrollment, tier celebration, expiry without promo collision.',
      'Reads tier property before sends.',
      'Measure enrolled LTV lift.',
      ],
    },
    {
      slug: 'klaviyo',
      rank: 4,
      paragraphs: [
      'Klaviyo tier segmentation and loyalty campaign reporting.',
      'RFM integration with tier status.',
      'Coordinate segments with Marsello rules.',
      ],
    },
];
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={desc} site={site} path={path}>
  <ArticleSchema title={title} description={desc} siteName={site.name} domain={site.domain} path={path} />
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/use-cases" class="link text-sm">← Use-case playbooks</a>
      <span class="badge mt-6">Marketing stack playbook</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title mt-5 max-w-5xl">Shopify marketing stack for {useCaseName}</h1>
      <p class="mt-7 max-w-3xl text-xl text-cyan-100">{heroSubtitle}</p>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">Trigger: {trigger} · Timing: {timing}</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="container pb-12">
    <TldrBox title={`Stack picks for ${useCaseName}`} picks={tldrPicks} />
    <article class="prose-shopify mb-12 card">
      <h2>Stack execution playbook</h2>
  <p>Loyalty is not a standalone app install — it is a stack layer that must coordinate with lifecycle email, SMS, capture popups, and promotional calendars. Points emails firing the same day as sitewide sale emails train subscribers to ignore both.</p>
  <p>Enrollment timing: second full-price order for most DTC, not first-order discount hunters. Profile property loyalty_enrolled gates all points creative — first-time buyers see product education not empty points balance.</p>
  <p>Tier achievement triggers immediate celebration email from Sequenzy with Marsello tier sync — then suppress promotional sends for 48h to let celebration land.</p>
  <p>Points expiring sequences start 30 days before expiry, 7 days before, final day — each suppressed if customer redeemed or if conflicting BFCM promo active per collision calendar.</p>
  <p>VIP early access is loyalty value without discount — early collection access for gold tier beats double points during sale week when margin is already compressed.</p>
  <p>Yotpo Loyalty suits brands already on Yotpo reviews wanting consolidation. Marsello adds POS integration for omnichannel retailers on Shopify plus physical store.</p>
  <p>SMS for loyalty: points expiry only for opted-in VIPs — not weekly points balance spam.</p>
  <p>Wholesale, employees, and one-time discount-only buyers excluded from enrollment automations.</p>
  <p>Loyalty + reviews synergy: bonus points for photo review submission — coordinated in Yotpo with single email announcement via Sequenzy, not separate review ask and points ask same week.</p>
  <p>Analytics: enrollment rate, repeat purchase frequency post-enrollment, redemption rate, tier progression speed, margin on loyalty-driven orders vs promo-driven.</p>
  <p>Failure mode: loyalty pitch to subscribers who never made second purchase — feels irrelevant and increases unsubscribe.</p>
  <p>Fix promotional collision calendar before loyalty launch — loyalty layer sits on top of governance, not instead of it.</p>

      <h2>Merchant scenarios</h2>
  <p><strong>Fashion early access:</strong> Gold tier gets drop preview 24h early via Sequenzy; no extra 10% off. Marsello tier sync. Promotional sale suppresses early access overlap.</p>
  <p><strong>Beauty replenishment + points:</strong> Points earned on full-price replenishment only. Sequenzy replenishment and points expiry share suppression rules.</p>
  <p><strong>Pet third-order enroll:</strong> Marsello enrolls on third order. Welcome-to-loyalty explains autoship bonus. Subscription SKU excluded from double points.</p>
  <p><strong>Home room completer VIP:</strong> Klaviyo segment completed 3+ room categories → manual VIP tier → early access seasonal refresh.</p>
  <p><strong>POD skip loyalty:</strong> Thin margin POD — no points program; community early access list instead of Marsello.</p>
  <p><strong>B2B exclude:</strong> Wholesale tags skip all loyalty automations — volume pricing replaces points.</p>

      <h2>Stack checklist</h2>
      <ul>
    <li>Enrollment trigger defined (typically 2nd+ full-price order)</li>
    <li>Discount-only one-time buyers excluded from enrollment</li>
    <li>Tier celebration suppresses promo 48h</li>
    <li>Points expiry series with 30d and 7d touches</li>
    <li>Collision calendar entry for loyalty vs sitewide promos</li>
    <li>Empty points module hidden in email templates</li>
    <li>Review-for-points coordinated single announcement</li>
    <li>Wholesale and employee exclusions verified</li>
    <li>Redemption does not stack with active popup code</li>
    <li>SMS loyalty limited to expiry urgency opted-in VIPs</li>
    <li>POS sync tested if Marsello omnichannel</li>
    <li>Monthly redemption and margin report</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Exclusions (non-negotiable)</h3>
      <ul>
    <li>Discount-only one-time buyers</li>
    <li>Wholesale accounts</li>
    <li>Employees</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Metrics that prove quality</h3>
      <ul>
    <li>Loyalty enrollment rate</li>
    <li>Repeat purchase frequency</li>
    <li>Points redemption rate</li>
    <li>Tier progression speed</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Common mistakes</h3>
      <ul>
    <li>Loyalty pitch to one-time discount buyers</li>
    <li>Points expiring without warning</li>
    <li>Loyalty emails duplicating promotional sends</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Loyalty layer in the six-layer stack</h2>
  <div>
    <h3>Loyalty engine: Marsello, Yotpo Loyalty</h3>
    <p>Points earn/burn, tiers, rewards catalog.</p>
    <p>Earn rules exclude clearance; bonus for reviews coordinated.</p>
    <p><strong>Failure mode:</strong> Points on already-discounted SKUs eroding margin.</p>
    <p><strong>Operator test:</strong> Margin on loyalty orders vs promo orders monthly.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3>Lifecycle orchestration: Sequenzy</h3>
    <p>Enrollment welcome, tier celebration, expiry warnings, VIP early access sends.</p>
    <p>Reads loyalty tier property before every promo send.</p>
    <p><strong>Failure mode:</strong> Promo email + double points same day.</p>
    <p><strong>Operator test:</strong> Collision audit — zero overlap last sale week.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3>Segmentation: Klaviyo</h3>
    <p>Tier segments for campaign coordination and reporting.</p>
    <p>VIP excluded from bargain hunter promos automatically.</p>
    <p><strong>Failure mode:</strong> Gold tier receives same 25% off as prospect.</p>
    <p><strong>Operator test:</strong> Tier-specific campaign performance tracked.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3>Proof coordination: Yotpo</h3>
    <p>Review-for-points campaigns in unified comms.</p>
    <p>Single email CTA for review + bonus points.</p>
    <p><strong>Failure mode:</strong> Review ask Monday, points promo Tuesday.</p>
    <p><strong>Operator test:</strong> Review submission rate during points campaigns.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3>SMS urgency: Postscript</h3>
    <p>Points expiry final 48h for opted-in VIP only.</p>
    <p>Max one loyalty SMS per quarter per subscriber.</p>
    <p><strong>Failure mode:</strong> Weekly points balance texts.</p>
    <p><strong>Operator test:</strong> SMS opt-out during expiry campaign under 1.5%.</p>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3>Analytics: Shopify, Marsello</h3>
    <p>Enrollment %, repeat frequency, redemption, LTV delta enrolled vs not.</p>
    <p>Holdout group not enrolled — measure true lift.</p>
    <p><strong>Failure mode:</strong> Points liability growing without repeat lift.</p>
    <p><strong>Operator test:</strong> Enrolled cohort LTV vs control at 180 days.</p>
  </div>

      <h2>Timing and trigger governance</h2>
  <p>Enroll after order 2 fulfilled — not at signup.</p>
  <p>Tier celebration within 1 hour of tier change event.</p>
  <p>Expiry warnings at -30d, -7d, -1d — skip if redeemed.</p>
  <p>Pause loyalty campaigns during BFCM unless early access is the offer.</p>

      <h2>Measurement across the stack</h2>
  <p>Enrollment rate of eligible repeat buyers.</p>
  <p>Repeat purchase frequency enrolled vs not.</p>
  <p>Redemption rate and points liability trend.</p>
  <p>Margin on loyalty-attributed orders.</p>

      <h2>Related playbooks</h2>
  <p>Integration: <a class="link" href="/guides/loyalty-integration">loyalty integration guide</a>.</p>
  <p>VIP: <a class="link" href="/use-cases/vip-segments">VIP segments</a>.</p>
  <p>Proof: <a class="link" href="/use-cases/reviews-and-ugc">reviews and UGC</a>.</p>

