<h2>FAQ deep dives</h2>
<p><strong>Best loyalty stack for Shopify?</strong> Marsello or Yotpo Loyalty as engine, Sequenzy for enrollment/expiry orchestration, Klaviyo tier segments, collision calendar with promotional layer. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
